project.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-68541349.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-68541349.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22''Very%20Scary''%3A%20Kerala%20Doctor%20Loses%20Money%2C%20Passport%20To%20Pickpockets%20In%20Italy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELosing%20a%20wallet%2C%20or%20a%20passport%20in%20a%20foreign%20country%20can%20truly%20be%20a%20terrifying%20and%20stressful%20experience.%20Recently%2C%20a%20couple%20from%20Kerala%20went%20through%20the%20same%20after%20they%20lost%20their%20passports%2C%20credit%20cards%2C%20and%20cash%20to%20pickpockets%20in%20Milan%2C%20Italy.%20Notably%2C%20Jothydev%20Kesavadev%2C%20a%20physician%20and%20diabetes%20researcher%2C%20and%20his%20wife%20Sunitha%20visited%20the%20country%20to%20present%20a%20research%20paper%20in%20Florence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20happened%20on%20March%205%20when%20the%20couple%20was%C2%A0entering%20Milan%20Central%20railway%20station%20in%20Italy%20to%20take%20a%20train%20to%20Florence.%20On%20the%20way%2C%20%26quot%3Ba%20tall%2C%20lean%20African-American%20man%26quot%3B%20bumped%20into%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''His%20large%20trolley%20bag%20hit%20my%20right%20knee%20and%20I%20almost%20fell.%20My%20wife%2C%20out%20of%20shock%20forgot%20the%20surroundings%20and%20bent%20down%20to%20help%20me%20out.%20When%20I%20looked%20back%20I%20saw%20a%20woman%20passing%20by%20her%20and%20then%20the%20woman%20and%20the%20man%20disappeared%20instantly%2C''%20Mr%C2%A0Kesavade%20wrote%20in%20a%20lengthy%20X%20post%20narrating%20the%20incident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20when%20his%20wife%20opened%20her%20handbag%2C%20she%20realised%20that%20her%20wallet%20containing%20the%20passports%2C%20credit%20and%20debit%20cards%20and%20cash%20was%20missing.%20They%20rushed%20to%20the%20police%20station%20and%20after%20a%20long%20wait%2C%20the%20cop%20prepared%20an%20FIR%20and%20asked%20them%20to%C2%A0contact%20the%20Indian%20Consulate%20in%20Milan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20morning%2C%20they%20reached%20out%20to%20their%20family%20friend%20and%20MP%20Shashi%20Tharoor.%20''His%20response%20was%20quick%20and%20powerful.%20Immense%20gratitude%20to%20SC.%20He%20immediately%20informed%20the%20Indian%20consulate%20in%20Italy%20and%20by%209%3A00%20AM%20%C2%A0I%20received%20a%20call%20from%20there.%20Consulate%20General%20Shri.Atul%20Chawhan%2C%20consoled%20us%20and%20promised%20an%20emergency%20passport%20for%20both%20of%20us%2C''%20the%20doctor%20further%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20the%20tweet%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EDear%20Friends%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnWe%20have%20a%20bitter%20story%20to%20share%20from%20Milan%2C%20Italy.%20Our%20passports%2C%20money%20and%20credit%20cards%20were%20stolen%20on%20March%205%2C%202024.%20Sunitha%20and%20I%20were%20just%20entering%20the%20Milan%20Central%20railway%20station%2C%20Italy%2C%20to%20take%20a%20train%20to%20Florence%2C%20to%20attend%20%26amp%3B%20present%20our%20research%20papers%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FitQN7sP9zZ%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FitQN7sP9zZ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Jothydev%20Kesavadev%20(%40jothydev)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjothydev%2Fstatus%2F1766932198597247187%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2010%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Upon%20arrival%20at%20the%20Consul%2C%20the%20officers%20were%20very%20courteous%20and%20offered%20us%20a%20warm%20welcome.%20Within%20an%20hour%20they%20provided%20us%20with%20two%20emergency%20passports%20and%20gave%20us%20the%20confidence%20to%20go%20back%20to%20India%20only%20after%20the%20meetings%20and%20presentations%20in%20Florence.%20Dear%20friends%20let%20me%20tell%20you%2C%20losing%20the%20passport%20and%20money%20in%20a%20foreign%20country%20is%20very%20very%20scary%20and%20a%20fearful%20experience%2C''%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kesavadev%20shared%20that%20the%20incident%20left%20them%20feeling%20shaken%20and%C2%A0guilty.%20%26quot%3BProbably%20due%20to%20repeated%20travels%20over%20several%20decades%20we%20were%20so%20careless%20and%20this%20is%20a%20lesson%20to%20learn%20from%2C''%20he%20said.%20The%20doctor%20also%20noted%20that%20pickpocket%20crimes%20in%20Italy%20are%20very%20common%20and%20advised%20fellow%20tourists%20to%20be%20careful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''I%20am%20sharing%20this%20experience%20in%20social%20media%3B%20whether%20you%20are%20a%20traveller%20or%20not%2C%20inexperienced%20or%20experienced%2C%20could%20be%20of%20some%20help%2C''%20he%20concluded%20the%20post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShashi%20Tharoor%20also%20reacted%20to%20the%20post%20and%20said%2C%20''Glad%20it%20all%20worked%20out%20in%20the%20end%C2%A0%40jothydev!%20So%20pleased%20our%20consulate%20did%20what%20was%20needed%20so%20well.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EGlad%20it%20all%20worked%20out%20in%20the%20end%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjothydev%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40jothydev%3C%2Fa%3E%20!%20So%20pleased%20our%20consulate%20did%20what%20was%20needed%20so%20well.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMEAIndia%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40MEAIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F2pTt4DFd4u%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F2pTt4DFd4u%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20(%40ShashiTharoor)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FShashiTharoor%2Fstatus%2F1767133112910368904%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2011%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EPickpockets%20largely%20tend%20to%20target%20tourists%2C%20as%20they're%20often%20confused%2C%20a%20bit%20overwhelmed%2C%20and