step-by-step%20process%20to%20apply%20for%20citizenship%20under%20this%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Is%20Eligible%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPersons%20from%20Hindu%2C%20Sikh%2C%20Buddhist%2C%20Jain%2C%20Parsi%20or%20Christian%20communities%20from%20Afghanistan%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20Bangladesh%2C%20who%20entered%20India%20on%20or%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014%2C%20can%20seek%20citizenship%20under%20CAA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%20To%20Apply%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApplications%20for%20Indian%20citizenship%20can%20be%20made%20online%20on%20https%3A%2F%2Findiancitizenshiponline.nic.in.%20A%20mobile%20application%2C%20CAA-2019%2C%20is%20also%20in%20the%20works.%20This%20application%20will%20be%20submitted%20to%20an%20Empowered%20Committee%20through%20the%20District%20Level%20Committee%20headed%20by%20a%20designated%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Categories%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20online%20application%20process%20provides%20multiple%20categories%20under%20which%20an%20applicant%20can%20seek%20Indian%20citizenship.%20These%20include%3A%20(i)%20a%20person%20of%20Indian%20origin%20(ii)%20a%20person%20married%20to%20a%20citizen%20of%20India%20(iii)%20a%20minor%20child%20of%20an%20Indian%20citizen%20(iv)%20a%20person%20whose%20parents%20are%20Indian%20citizens%20(v)%20a%20person%20who%20or%20either%20of%20parents%20was%20a%20citizen%20of%20Independent%20India%20(vi)%20a%20person%20registered%20as%20Overseas%20Citizen%20of%20India%20Cardholder%20(vii)%20a%20person%20seeking%20citizenship%20by%20naturalisation%20-%20an%20adult%20registered%20as%20overseas%20citizen%20of%20India%20for%20five%20years%2C%20and%20who%20has%20been%20living%20in%20India%20for%20a%20year%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDocuments%20Required%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20applicant%20can%20submit%20any%20of%20the%20following%20documents%20while%20applying%20for%20Indian%20citizenship%20under%20CAA%3A%20(i)%20Copy%20of%20passport%20issued%20by%20Afghanistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20or%20Pakistan%20government%20(ii)%20birth%20certificate%20issued%20by%20a%20government%20authority%20in%20these%20countries%20(iii)%20educational%20certificate%20from%20a%20school%2Fcollege%2Fboard%20or%20university%20in%20Afghanistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20or%20Pakistan%20(iv)%20identity%20document%20of%20any%20kind%20issued%20by%20government%20authorities%20in%20these%20countries%20(v)%20residential%20permit%20issued%20by%20Foreigners%20Regional%20Registration%20Officer%20or%20Foreigners%20Registration%20Officer%20in%20India%20(vi)any%20licence%20issued%20by%20government%20authorities%20in%20these%20three%20countries%20(vii)%20land%20or%20tenancy%20records%20in%20these%20countries%20(viii)%20Any%20document%20that%20shows%20that%20either%20of%20the%20parents%20or%20grandparents%20or%20greatgrandparents%20of%20the%20applicant%20is%20or%20had%20been%20a%20citizen%20of%20these%20countries.%20In%20effect%2C%20any%20document%20issued%20by%20a%20government%20authority%20in%20Afghanistan%20or%20Bangladesh%20or%20Pakistan%20to%20establish%20that%20the%20applicant%20is%20from%20either%20of%20these%20countries%20is%20valid%20for%20the%20citizenship%20process.%20This%20applies%20even%20if%20the%20document%20is%20past%20its%20validity%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20To%20Prove%20When%20Applicant%20Entered%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20applicant%20will%20also%20need%20to%20prove%20that%20he%2Fshe%20entered%20India%20before%20the%20cut-off%20date%20of%20December%2031%2C%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20documents%20required%20for%20this%20include%3A%20(i)%20copy%20of%20the%20visa%20and%20immigration%20stamp%20on%20arrival%20(ii)%20registration%20certificate%20or%20residential%20permit%20issued%20by%20the%20Foreigners%20Regional%20Registration%20Officer%20or%20Foreigners%20Registration%20Officer%20(FRO)%20in%20India%20(iii)%20a%20slip%20issued%20by%20the%20Census%20enumerators%20in%20India%20during%20surveys%20(iv)%20government%20issued%20licence%20or%20certificate%20or%20permit%20in%20India%20(including%20driving%20licence%2C%20Aadhaar%20card%20etc.)%20(v)%20ration%20card%20issued%20in%20India%20(vi)%20any%20letter%20issued%20by%20the%20government%20or%20court%20to%20the%20applicant%20with%20official%20stamp%20(vii)%20birth%20certificate%20of%20the%20applicant%20issued%20in%20India%20(viii)%20land%20or%20tenancy%20records%20or%20registered%20rental%20agreement%20in%20India%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20applicant%20(ix)%20PAN%20card%20with%20the%20date%20of%20issue%20(x)%20any%20document%20issued%20by%20the%20Centre%20or%20state%20government%20or%20PSUs%20or%20other%20public%20authority%20(xi)%20certificate%20issued%20by%20an%20elected%20member%20of%20any%20rural%20or%20urban%20body%20or%20officer%20(xii)%20account%20details%20issued%20by%20the%20banks%2C%20including%20private%20banks%2C%20or%20post%20office%20accounts%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20applicant%20(xiii)%20insurance%20policies%20issued%20by%20companies%20in%20India%20in%20the%20applicant's%20name%20(xiv)%20electricity%20connection%20papers%20or%20bills%20or%20other%20utility%20bills%20in%20the%20applicant's%20name%20(xv)%20court%20or%20tribunal%20records%20in%20respect%20of%20the%20applicant%20(xvi)%20document%20showing%20employment%20in%20India%20supported%20by%20Employees%20Provident%20Fund%2F%20General%20Provident%20Fund%2F%20Pension%2F%20Employees'%20State%20Insurance%20Corporation%20(xvii)%20school-leaving%20certificate%20of%20the%20applicant%20issued%20in%20India%20(xviii)%20academic%20certificate%20issued%20by%20a%20school%20or%20college%20or%20university%20or%20government%20institution%20(xix)%20municipality%20trade%20licence%20(xx)%20marriage%20certificate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EApplication%20Submitted%2C%20What%20Next%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20application%2C%20the%20form%20will%20be%20examined%20by%20a%20district-level%20committee.%20This%20committee%20will%20then%20inform%20the%20applicant%20through%20email%2FSMS%20the%20date%20an%20time%20on%20which%20he%2Fshe%20will%20be%20required%20to%20visit%20in%20person%20with%20original%20documents.%20If%20all%20is%20in%20order%2C%20the%20designated%20officer%20will%20administer%20an%20%26quot%3Boath%20of%20allegiance%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20applicant.%20If%20anything%20is%20missing%2C%20the%20committee%20may%20ask%20the%20applicant%20to%20provide%20it.%20However%2C%20if%20the%20applicant%20does%20not%20appear%20before%20the%20committee%20despite%20%26quot%3Breasonable%20opportunities%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20district%20committee%20may%20the%20application%20to%20the%20Empowered%20Committee%20for%20refusal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20documents%20are%20in%20order%2C%20the%20designated%20officer%20will%20certify%20online%20that%20the%20papers%20are%20verified.%20The%20district%20committee%20will%20also%20upload%20the%20%26quot%3Boath%20of%20allegiance%26quot%3B%20and%20forward%20the%20application%20in%20electronic%20form%20to%20the%20empowered%20panel.%20This%20panel%20will%20then%20examine%20the%20case%20and%20approve%20or%20reject%20the%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Will%20Citizenship%20Certificate%20Be%20Issued%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20applicant%20will%20be%20issued%20a%20digital%20certificate.%20Ink-signed%20copy%20of%20the%20certificate%20will%20be%20issued%20only%20if%20the%20applicant%20has%20opted%20for%20it%20at%20the%20application%20stage.%20This%20certificate%20will%20have%20to%20be%20collected%20from%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Empowered%20Committee%20i.e.%20office%20of%20Director%20(Census%20operations)%20of%20State%2FUnion%20Territory%20concerned.%20For%20those%20granted%20citizenship%2C%20they%20will%20be%20considered%20Indian%20nationals%20from%20the%20date%20of%20their%20entry%20into%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20The%20Cost%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fee%20of%20Rs%2050%20is%20to%20be%20made%20online%20at%20the%20application%20stage.%20The%20government%20has%20not%20specified%20any%20other%20charge%20for%20the%20citizenship%20application%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710221640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fuj9njsbg_caa-rules_625x300_12_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcitizenship-amendment-act-how-to-apply-for-citizenship-under-new-law-key-questions-answered-5222785%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20the%20Centre%20issuing%20a%20notification%20for%20the%20contentious%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%2C%20non-Muslims%20migrants%20from%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20Afghanistan%20can%20now%20seek%20Indian%20citizenship%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcitizenship-amendment-act-how-to-apply-for-citizenship-under-new-law-key-questions-answered-5222785%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcitizenship-amendment-act-how-to-apply-for-citizenship-under-new-law-key-questions-answered-5222785%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcitizenship-amendment-act-how-to-apply-for-citizenship-under-new-law-key-questions-answered-5222785%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22All%20By%20Myself%20songwriter%20Eric%20Carmen%20dies%20aged%2074%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710221547000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FD8E9%2Fproduction%2F_132892555_ericcarmen.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68541053%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20singer-songwriter's%20hits%20also%20included%20Hungry%20Eyes%2C%20which%20featured%20in%20the%20Dirty%20Dancing%20movie.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A96%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F