nel%2C%20constructed%20on%20the%20road%20connecting%20Assam's%20Tezpur%20to%20West%20Kameng%20district%20of%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20is%20being%20billed%20as%20the%20longest%20bi-lane%20road%20tunnel%20in%20the%20world%20at%20such%20an%20altitude.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sela%20Tunnel%20will%20provide%20for%20better%20movement%20of%20troops%20and%20weaponry%20to%20various%20forward%20locations%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%20with%20China%2C%20according%20to%20military%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%2C%20which%20claims%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20as%20South%20Tibet%2C%20routinely%20objects%20to%20Indian%20leaders'%20visits%20to%20the%20state%20to%20highlight%20its%20claims.%20Beijing%20has%20also%20named%20the%20area%20as%20Zangnan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20repeatedly%20rejected%20China's%20territorial%20claims%20over%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20asserting%20that%20the%20state%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20country.%20New%20Delhi%20has%20also%20dismissed%20Beijing's%20move%20to%20assign%20%26quot%3Binvented%26quot%3B%20names%20to%20the%20area%2C%20saying%20it%20did%20not%20alter%20the%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20by%20the%20official%20media%20here%20about%20PM%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20at%20a%20media%20briefing%20here%20on%20Monday%2C%20Chinese%20Foreign%20Ministry%20spokesperson%20Wang%20Wenbin%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BChina%20strongly%20deplores%20and%20firmly%20opposes%20the%20Indian%20leader's%20visit%20to%20the%20East%20Section%20of%20the%20China-India%20boundary.%20We%20have%20made%20solemn%20representations%20to%20India.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeign%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20rejected%20the%20comments%20and%20said%20objecting%20to%20visits%20by%20Indian%20leaders%20does%20not%20stand%20to%20reason.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20reject%20the%20comments%20made%20by%20the%20Chinese%20side%20regarding%20the%20visit%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20Arunachal%20Pradesh.%20Indian%20leaders%20visit%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20as%20they%20visit%20other%20States%20of%20India.%20Objecting%20to%20such%20visits%20or%20India's%20developmental%20projects%20does%20not%20stand%20to%20reason.%20Further%2C%20it%20will%20not%20change%20the%20reality%20that%20the%20State%20of%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20was%2C%20is%2C%20and%20will%20always%20be%20an%20integral%20and%20inalienable%20part%20of%20India.%20Chinese%20side%20has%20been%20made%20aware%20of%20this%20consistent%20position%20on%20several%20occasions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710220500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Ffkkaif3_pm-modi_625x300_12_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchina-lodges-diplomatic-protest-with-india-over-pm-modis-arunachal-pradesh-visit-sela-tunnel-tawang-5222221%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China%20on%20Monday%20said%20it%20lodged%20a%20diplomatic%20protest%20with%20India%20over%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20last%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchina-lodges-diplomatic-protest-with-india-over-pm-modis-arunachal-pradesh-visit-sela-tunnel-tawang-5222221%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchina-lodges-diplomatic-protest-with-india-over-pm-modis-arunachal-pradesh-visit-sela-tunnel-tawang-5222221%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchina-lodges-diplomatic-protest-with-india-over-pm-modis-arunachal-pradesh-visit-sela-tunnel-tawang-5222221%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'England%20were%20lucky%20that%20Virat%20Kohli%20was%20unavailable...'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710220354000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-1