had%20raised%20safety%20concerns%20at%20the%20Charleston%20plant.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dol.gov%2Fagencies%2Foalj%2FPUBLIC%2FWHISTLEBLOWER%2FREFERENCES%2FREFERENCE_WORKS%2FAIR21%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20AIR21%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20law%20protecting%20airline%20safety%20whistleblowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarnett's%20lawyer%2C%20Brian%20Knowles%2C%20said%20the%20former%20Boeing%20manager%20was%20supposed%20to%20report%20for%20the%20third%20day%20of%20his%20deposition%20on%20Friday%2C%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.corporatecrimereporter.com%2Fnews%2F200%2Fboeing-whistleblower-found-dead-in-charleston-after-break-in-depositions%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECorporate%20Crime%20Reporter.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20questioned%20by%20Boeing's%20lawyers%20on%20Thursday%20and%20then%20cross-examined%20by%20Knowles%20on%20Friday%2C%20but%20didn't%20show%20up%20or%20respond%20to%20calls%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Knowles%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarnett's%20lawyers%20asked%20his%20hotel%20to%20check%20on%20the%20whistleblower%2C%20and%20he%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20his%20vehicle%2C%20Knowles%20told%20the%20Corporate%20Crime%20Reporter.%20The%20BBC%20reported%20the%20same%20details%20surrounding%20Barnett's%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnowles%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoeing%20has%2C%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20come%20under%20scrutiny%20over%20safety%20concerns%20in%20its%20737%20Max%20planes%20after%20an%20Alaska%20Airlines%20flight%20in%20January%20had%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffaa-investigation-boeing-alaska-airlines-door-plug-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edoor%20plug%20blown%20out%20of%20its%20fuselage%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20in%20the%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F03%2F