ref%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIndiaUNNewYork%2Fstatus%2F1767276993882595537%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2011%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20last%20year%2C%20China%20had%20put%20a%20technical%20hold%20on%20the%20proposal%20after%20India%20and%20the%20United%20States%20submitted%20a%20proposal%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council's%20(UNSC)%201267%20Al%20Qaeda%20Sanctions%20Committee%20to%20designate%20Sajid%20Mir%2C%20who%20is%20wanted%20for%20his%20involvement%20in%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks%2C%20which%20killed%20166%20people%20and%20injured%20over%20300.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20had%20effectively%20blocked%20a%20proposal%20to%20designate%20Pakistan-based%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-genuine-will-to-sincerely-fight-terrorism-india-on-china-blocking-un-listing-of-pak-based-terrorist-sajid-mir-4138944%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELashkar-e-Taiba%20(LeT)%20terrorist%20Sajid%20Mir%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20global%20terrorist.%20For%20a%20proposal%20to%20be%20adopted%2C%20it%20needs%20consensus%20from%20all%20the%20member%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20Permanent%20Representative%20to%20the%20UN%20Kamboj%20argued%20that%20the%20selection%20of%20chairs%20of%20subsidiary%20bodies%20and%20decision-making%20power%20must%20be%20given%20through%20an%20open%20process%20that%20intends%20to%20be%20transparent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20selection%20of%20chairs%20of%20subsidiary%20bodies%20and%20distribution%20of%20pen%20holderships%20must%20be%20made%20through%20a%20process%20which%20is%20open%2C%20which%20is%20transparent%2C%20which%20is%20based%20on%20exhaustive%20consultations%20and%20with%20a%20more%20integrated%20perspective.%20The%20consensus%20of%20the%20e%20ten%20on%20chairs%20of%20subsidiary%20bodies%2C%20to%20be%20assumed%20by%20the%20E-10%20themselves%2C%20must%20be%20absolutely%20honoured%20by%20the%20P-5%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20troop-contributing%20countries%2C%20my%20delegation%20would%20like%20to%20reiterate%20that%20the%20concerns%20of%20the%20troop%20and%20police%20contributing%20countries%20should%20be%20taken%20into%20consideration%20for%20better%20implementation%20of%20peacekeeping%20mandates.%20There%20is%20a%20need%20to%20review%20the%20agenda%20of%20the%20council%20and%20remove%20obsolete%20and%20irrelevant%20items%20from%20the%20agenda%20of%20the%20Security%20Council%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20also%20reiterated%20its%20call%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-s-jaishankar-was-asked-about-un-permanent-seat-raisina-dialogue-2024-his-witty-response-leave-it-to-bcci-5113731%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUNSC%20reforms%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20asked%20countries%20that%20block%20the%20revision%20of%20giving%20permanent%20seats%20at%20the%20forum%20to%20contribute%20to%20making%20the%20council%20fit%20for%20the%2021st%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20threats%20to%20international%20peace%20and%20security%20evolve%2C%20Mr.%20President%2C%20so%20must%20this%20council.%20We%20ask%20those%20blocking%20progress%20on%20this%20vital%20issue%20to%20heed%20calls%20for%20genuine%20reform%20and%20contribute%20to%20making%20this%20council%20truly%20fit%20for%20purpose%20for%20the%2021st%20century.%20Thank%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Kamboj%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20also%20imperative%20to%20note%20that%20working%20methods%20do%20not%20stand%20in%20isolation%20as%20they%20have%20an%20organic%20linkage%20to%20other%20clusters%2C%20including%20the%20relationship%20with%20the%20General%20Assembly%20and%20discussions%20on%20the%20veto.%20Therefore%2C%20unless%20we%20address%20the%20issue%20in%20its%20entirety%2C%20a%20piecemeal%20approach%20would%20fail%20to%20offer%20a%20holistic%20solution%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5