s%20name.%20It%20means%20'beloved'%20in%20Spanish%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMendes%20also%20discussed%20the%20couple's%20decision%20to%20keep%20her%20child's%20life%20as%20private%20as%20possible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhether%20we%20like%20it%20or%20not%2C%20privacy%20is%20going%20to%20be%20very%20difficult%20for%20Esmeralda.%20I%20think%20it's%20unfair%20but%20that's%20our%20reality.%20So%20Ryan%20and%20I%20decided%20early%20on%20to%20give%20her%20as%20much%20privacy%20as%20we%20could.%20And%20my%20pregnancy%20was%20the%20first%20opportunity%20to%20give%20her%20that.%20It's%20such%20an%20intimate%20time%20for%20the%20mother%2C%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20that%20it%20seems%20all%20very%20innocuous%20when%20you're%20flipping%20through%20a%20tabloid%20at%20the%20doctor's%20office%20or%20see%20a%20photo%20of%20a%20pregnant%20lady%20online%2C%20but%20I%20find%20the%20media's%20'bump%20watch'%20obsession%20to%20be%20both%20intrusive%20and%20stressful.%20So%20I%20made%20a%20decision%20to%20eject%20myself%20from%20it%20completely.%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'Annnnd%20I'm%20out.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EApril%202015%3A%20Mendes%20stars%20in%20%26quot%3BLost%20River%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20film%20that%20Gosling%20directed%20and%20co-produced.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22992%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22eva%20%20lost%20river%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5eb040893dac9a018b494c92%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22744%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEva%20Mendes%20starred%20in%20%26quot%3BLost%20River.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EBold%20Films%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMendes%20played%20a%20cabaret%20dancer%20in%20the%202015%20film%20%26quot%3BLost%20River%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20was%20Gosling's%20feature%20film%20directorial%20debut.%20It%20marked%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20couple%20worked%20together%20after%20%26quot%3BThe%20Place%20Beyond%20the%20Pines.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%202019%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oprahmag.com%2Fstyle%2Fa27409832%2Feva-mendes-new-york-and-company-collection-daughters%2F%5C%22%3EOprah%20Magazine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mendes%20reminisced%20on%20her%20experience%20working%20with%20her%20partner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20two%20times%20we've%20collaborated%2C%20him%20and%20I%2C%20have%20been%20the%20two%20best%20experiences%20in%20my%20career.%20There's%20such%20special%20work%20in%20'The%20Place%20Beyond%20the%20Pines.'%20We%20had%20known%20each%20other%20for%20a%20while%20already%2C%20so%20to%20work%20together%20was%20really%20exciting%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMendes%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BAnd%20being%20in%20the%20film%20'Lost%20River'%20was%20nothing%20short%20of%20a%20magical%20experience.%20I%20would%20love%20to%20either%20act%20opposite%20him%20again%20or%20be%20directed%20by%20him%20at%20some%20point.%20I%20just%20love%20working%20with%20him.%20In%20a%20career%20of%2020%2B%20years%2C%20to%20have%20my%20two%20most%20incredible%20creative%20experiences%20be%20with%20him%2C%20of%20course%2C%20I'd%20want%20a%20third.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDecember%202015%3A%20Gosling%20speaks%20about%20his%20daughter%20before%20adding%20that%20there's%20%26quot%3Bnothing%20else%26quot%3B%20for%20him%20except%20for%20Mendes.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221161%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ryan%20Gosling%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5eb044a53dac9a03c7155dd3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22871%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERyan%20Gosling%20shares%20two%20daughters%20with%20Eva%20Mendes.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%2F%20Astrid%20Stawiarz%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20be%20our%20first%20Christmas%20where%20Esmeralda%20is%20sort%20of%20taking%20it%20all%20in%2C%20so%20that's%20exciting%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20actor%20said%20during%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fca.hellomagazine.com%2Fcelebrities%2F02015120320832%2Fexclusive-ryan-gosling-on-esmeralda-s-first-christmas-and-devotion-to-eva-mendes%5C%22%3EHello!%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BShe's%20obsessed%20with%20the%20Hanson%20Christmas%20album!%20No%20disrespect%20to%20Hanson%2C%20they're%20very%20talented%20kids%2C%20but%20I%20think%20I've%20heard%20that%20record%20enough.%20I'm%20sure%20it%20will%20be%20on%20a%20loop%20this%20Christmas%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGosling%20also%20gushed%20about%20Mendes%20during%20the%20interview%2C%20saying%20that%20there's%20%26quot%3Bnothing%20else%26quot%3B%20out%20there%20for%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20that%20I'm%20with%20the%20person%20I'm%20supposed%20to%20be%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20continuing%20to%20say%20that%20the%20only%20criteria%20he%20seeks%20in%20a%20woman%20is%20%26quot%3Bthat%20she's%20Eva%20Mendes.%20There's%20nothing%20else%20I'm%20looking%20for.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EApril%202016%3A%20They%20welcome%20their%20second%20child.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ryan%20gosling%20eva%20mendes%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5eb046693dac9a04a8650d13%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERyan%20Gosling%20and%20Eva%20Mendes%20have%20two%20kids.%3Cp%3EVera%20Anderson%C2%A0%2F%C2%A0Getty%20Images%3B%20Alexander%20Tamargo%C2%A0%2F%C2%A0Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tmz.com%2F2016%2F05%2F09%2Feva-mendes-ryan-gosling-baby-born-birth-certificate%2F%5C%22%3ETMZ%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20Mendes%20gave%20birth%20to%20her%20second%20daughter%20in%20Santa%20Monica%2C%20California.%20The%20actors%20named%20their%20second%20daughter%20Amada%20Lee%2C%20whose%20first%20name%20is%20the%20same%20as%20their%20eldest%20daughter's%20middle%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hellomagazine.com%2Fhealthandbeauty%2Fmother-and-baby%2F2016080332780%2Feva-mendes-explains-daughters-name%2F%5C%22%3ELatina%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mendes%20opened%20up%20about%20the%20couple's%20tie%20to%20the%20name.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20grandmother's%20name%20is%20Amada%2C%20and%20Esmeralda%20Amada%20is%20the%20name%20of%20our%20oldest%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20a%20few%20names%20picked%20out%20for%20our%20new%20baby%2C%20and%20when%20she%20was%20born%2C%20we%20didn't%20feel%20like%20those%20names%20were%20her.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20some%20people%20may%20be%20surprised%20that%20Gosling%20and%20Mendes%20reused%20the%20name%2C%20the%20Cuban%20actor%20said%20that%20it's%20not%20abnormal%20in%20her%20culture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20true%20Latin%20fashion%2C%20we%20reuse%20names%20all%20the%20time.%20I%20actually%20told%20Ryan%2C%20'This%20is%20common%20in%20Latin%20culture%2C%20so%20it%20wouldn't%20be%20crazy.'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJanuary%202017%3A%20Gosling%20wins%20a%20Golden%20Globe%20award%20and%20dedicates%20it%20to%20Mendes.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221941%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ryan%20gosling%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5eb048ff1441920a681f92c4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221455%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERyan%20Gosling%20starred%20in%20the%20movie%20%26quot%3BLa%20La%20Land.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENBC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGosling%20won%20best%20actor%20in%20a%20musical%20or%20comedy%20at%20the%202017%20Golden%20Globes%20for%20his%20performance%20in%20%26quot%3BLa%20La%20Land.%26quot%3B%20Although%20Mendes%20didn't%20accompany%20Gosling%20to%20the%20ceremony%2C%20he%20dedicated%20the%20award%20to%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to