3Cp%3EThe%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20president%E2%80%99s%C2%A0prophecy%20about%20his%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20counterpart%20and%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20has%20fallen%20on%20its%20face%20with%20the%20latter%20going%20solo%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20state.%20It%E2%80%99s%20to%20be%20seen%20to%20what%20extent%20his%20prediction%20regarding%20the%20BJP%20comes%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanerjee%20was%20a%20founder%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20and%20was%20quite%20loquacious%2C%20at%20least%2C%20in%20her%20words%20against%20the%20Hindutva%20party.%20But%20her%20move%2C%20according%20to%20political%20pundits%2C%20has%20decidedly%20helped%20the%20BJP%20in%20breaking%20the%20larger%20opposition%20unity%20on%20the%20Bengal%20turf.%20The%20eastern%20state%20now%20is%20all%20set%20to%20witness%20a%20triangular%20contest%20between%20the%20BJP%2C%20TMC%20and%20the%20Congress-Left%20to%20an%20obvious%20advantage%20of%20the%20party%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TMC%20chief%20landed%20in%20Patna%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20first%20oppositions%E2%80%99%20meet%20on%20June%2023%2C%202023%2C%20went%20straight%20to%20Yadav%20and%20bowed%20before%20him.%20The%20picture%20of%20Yadav%20tapping%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20head%20in%20a%20display%20of%20affection%20and%20the%20West%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20describing%20Yadav%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Chighly%20respected%20senior%20pro%E2%80%9D%20fuelled%20a%20perception%20among%20the%20beleaguered%20opposition%20leaders%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfiery%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EDidi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(sister)%20and%20%E2%80%9Cindomitable%E2%80%9D%20Yadav%20together%20would%20effectively%20challenge%20the%20Hindutva%20party%20in%20Bengal%20and%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20perception%20stands%20demolished%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Choudhary%20is%20quoted%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Findia-bloc-collapse-west-bengal-adhir-ranjan-chowdhury-mamata-banerjee-9206712%2F%5C%22%3Esaying%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CShe%20(Banerjee)%20thinks%20the%20Central%20government%20would%20send%20ED%2C%20CBI%E2%80%A6after%20the%20TMC%E2%80%A6%20So%2C%20she%20chose%20to%20stay%20out%20of%20alliance%20and%20send%20a%20message%20to%20the%20PMO%20that%20she%20is%20not%20part%20of%20the%20alliance%E2%80%A6and%20that%20she%20is%20not%20fighting%20the%20BJP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20hard%20to%20measure%20the%20truth%20of%20Choudhary%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20but%20the%20fact%20remains%20that%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20nephew%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20and%20several%20of%20her%20party%20leaders%20are%20under%20the%20scanner%20of%20the%20central%20investigating%20agencies%20and%20many%20of%20her%20former%20party%20colleagues%20including%20Shubhendu%20Adhikari%20have%20shifted%20to%20the%20BJP%20to%20%E2%80%9Csave%20their%20skin%E2%80%9D%20in%20corruption%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frjds-jan-vishwas-patna-rally-turns-into-a-big-india-push-first-in-hindi-belt-in-2024%5C%22%3ERJD%E2%80%99s%20Jan%20Vishwas%20Patna%20Rally%20Turns%20Into%20a%20Big%20INDIA%20Push%2C%20First%20in%20Hindi%20Belt%20in%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20former%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20judge%20Abhijit%20Gangopadhyay%E2%80%99s%20joining%20the%20BJP%20is%20being%20linked%20to%20his%20orders%20against%20TMC%20leaders%20in%20cases%20of%20corruption%20which%20he%20had%20passed%20in%20his%20capacity%20as%20a%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHow%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20and%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20are%20different%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20comes%20the%20difference%20between%20Yadav%20and%20Banerjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20agencies%20have%20been%20relentless%20against%20the%20RJD%20president%20and%20his%20family%20members%20for%20years.%20He%20stayed%20in%20jail%20for%20four%20years%20with%20the%20CBI%20ferociously%20opposing%20his%20bail%20from%20the%20lower%20court%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigating%20agencies%E2%80%99%20heat%20on%20him%20and%20his%20family%20members%20increased%20manifold%20with%20Modi%20coming%20to%20power%20in%202014.%20The%20CBI%20dug%20the%20cases%20related%20to%20his%20tenures%20as%20the%20railway%20minister%20(2004-2009)%20which%20it%20had%20closed%20in%202011%20and%20framed%20his%20son%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20wife%20Rabri%20Devi%20and%20their%20daughters%20in%20corruption%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20at%20no%20point%20of%20time%2C%20Yadav%20ever%20gave%20the%20slightest%20hint%20to%20play%20ball%20with%20the%20BJP.%20Rather%2C%20the%20more%20the%20investigating%20agencies%20stepped%20up%20their%20pressure%2C%20the%20more%20rebellious%20he%20became.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CAgar%20Lalu%20ji%20BJP%20se%20haath%20milaa%20lete%20tou%20wo%20aaj%20Hinustan%20ke%20raja%20Harishchandra%20hot-e.%20Tathakathit%20chara%20ghotala%20do%20minute%20mein%20bhaichara%20ghotala%20ho%20jata%20agar%20Lalu%20ji%20ka%20DNA%20badal%20jaataa%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20a%20pinned%20tweet%20of%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20posted%20on%20December%2026%2C%202017%2C%20reads.%20In%20English%2C%20it%20means%20that%20had%20Lalu%20joined%20the%20BJP%20he%20would%20have%20been%20treated%20like%20the%20truthful%20king%20Harishchandra%20and%20would%20have%20been%20exonerated%20from%20all%20the%20charges%20of%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%82%20%E0%A4%9C%E0%A5%80%20BJP%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A5%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%8B%20%E0%A4%B5%E0%A5%8B%20%E