ack%20on%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20officials%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI).%20This%20decision%20keeps%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%2C%20accused%20of%20instigating%20the%20attack%2C%20in%20CBI%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%205%2C%20the%20high%20court%20had%20transferred%20the%20investigation%20solely%20to%20the%20CBI%20and%20directed%20Shahjahan%E2%80%99s%20transfer%20to%20their%20custody.%20The%20West%20Bengal%20government%20challenged%20the%20order%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20apex%20court%2C%20in%20its%20verdict%2C%20upheld%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20decision%20on%20the%20CBI%20investigation%20and%20questioned%20the%20state%20government%20why%20it%20took%2050%20days%20to%20arrest%20Shahjahan.%20However%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20removed%20critical%20remarks%20made%20by%20the%20high%20court%20against%20the%20state%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20of%20Justices%20B.R.%20Gavai%20and%20Sandeep%20Mehta%20ordered%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20inclined%20to%20interfere%20with%20the%20impugned%20order.%20Observations%20against%20state%20police%20and%20West%20Bengal%20government%20to%20be%20expunged.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%20Shahjahan%20was%20a%20key%20accused%20in%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%20PDS%20scam%20in%20Bengal.%20A%20close%20associate%20of%20arrested%20TMC%20minister%20Jyotipriya%20Mallick%2C%20he%20came%20into%20the%20spotlight%20earlier%20this%20year%20when%20the%20ED%20officials%20faced%20a%20mob%20attack%20during%20a%20raid%20on%20his%20residence%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20in%20North%2024%20Paragans.%20%C2%A0The%20incident%20sparked%20a%20series%20of%20legal%20manoeuvres.%20The%20state%20police%20filed%20a%20case%20initially%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20complaint%20from%20the%20ED.%20Interestingly%2C%20Shahjahan%E2%80%99s%20caretaker%20also%20lodged%20a%20counter-complaint%20against%20the%20ED%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20large%20number%20of%20women%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20had%20accused%20Trinamool%20Congress%20strongman%20Shajahan%20Sheikh%20and%20his%20supporters%20of%20%E2%80%9Cland-grab%20and%20sexual%20assault%E2%80%9D%20under%20coercion.%20Shahjahan%20continues%20to%20evade%20arrest%2C%20with%20both%20state%20police%20and%20central%20agencies%20unable%20to%20trace%20him.%20Following%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20intervention%2C%20he%20was%20arrested%20on%20February%2029%20by%20the%20state%20police%20which%20the%20opposition%20party%20termed%20as%20staged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20can%20I%20say%20about%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20action%3F%20This%20is%20really%20shameful%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20political%20analyst%20Biswanath%20Chakraborty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficially%2C%20TMC%20is%20maintaining%20a%20wait-and-see%20approach.%20Sandeshkhali%20MLA%20Sukumar%20Mahato%2C%20known%20to%20be%20close%20to%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20party%20would%20look%20into%20the%20matter%20and%20take%20further%20steps.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20Bengali%20original%20by%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710171724000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13112624%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-13-at-11.25.27-AM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsandeshkhali-case-sc-rejects-bengal-govts-plea-against-calcutta-hc-order-of-cbi-probe%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20decision%20keeps%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%2C%20accused%20of%20instigating%20the%20attack%2C%20in%20CBI%20custody.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsandeshkhali-case-sc-rejects-bengal-govts-plea-against-calcutta-hc-order-of-cbi-probe%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre%20to%20develop%20non-personal%20data%