Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Amit%20Shah%20(Modi%20Ka%20Parivar)%20(%40AmitShah)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAmitShah%2Fstatus%2F1767192979197104180%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2011%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20without%20rules%20being%20framed%2C%20the%20Act%20could%20not%20be%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20in%20a%20statement%20released%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20had%20said%2C%C2%A0%E2%80%9CThe%20applications%20(for%20citizenship)%20will%20be%20submitted%20in%20a%20completely%20online%20mode%20for%20which%20a%20web%20portal%20has%20been%20provided%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAA%20aims%20to%20provide%20citizenship%20to%20Hindus%2C%20Parsis%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Buddhists%2C%20Jains%20and%20Christians%20purportedly%20fleeing%20persecution%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20Muslim-majority%20neighbours%20%E2%80%93%20namely%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20Afghanistan%20and%20Bangladesh%20%E2%80%93%20and%20who%20arrived%20in%20India%20before%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exclusion%20of%20Muslims%20from%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20legislation%20and%20fears%20that%20it%20would%20disenfranchise%20many%20Muslims%20in%20India%20when%20combined%20with%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%20had%20drawn%20widespread%20protests%20from%20thousands%20of%20citizens%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20protests%20and%20violence%20that%20ensued%2C%20the%20government%20notified%20the%20law%20in%20January%20December%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHome%20affairs%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20last%20month%20that%20the%20rules%20for%20the%20CAA%20would%20be%20notified%20before%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20which%20are%20expected%20to%20take%20place%20between%20April%20and%20May%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoments%20after%20the%20home%20affairs%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20statement%20on%20X%2