I%20belong%20to%20a%20lower%20middle%20class%20family%20in%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20used%20to%20work%20at%20Taj%20Bengal%20Hotel%20in%20Kolkata%20until%20my%20contract%20came%20to%20an%20end%20in%20June%202023%2C%20and%20rendered%20me%20unemployed.%20My%20father%20fell%20ill%20around%20the%20same%20time%20and%20I%20spent%20all%20my%20savings%20on%20his%20treatment.%20I%20was%20desperate%20for%20a%20job%20when%20I%20came%20across%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBRX7LQio2Sg%5C%22%3Evideos%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20a%20Youtube%20channel%20named%20%E2%80%98Baba%20Vlogs%E2%80%99%2C%20run%20by%20a%20visa%20agent%20who%20offers%20assistance%20in%20getting%20jobs%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%20he%20spoke%20about%20job%20vacancies%20of%20helpers%20in%20the%20Russian%20Army%2C%20with%20a%20monthly%20salary%20of%20Rs%2040%2C000.%20He%20further%20said%20that%20this%20job%20will%20make%20applicants%20eligible%20for%20a%20Russian%20passport%2C%20which%20in%20turn%2C%20would%20open%20gates%20for%20opportunities%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20found%20it%20to%20be%20a%20lucrative%20offer%20and%20thought%20that%20this%20could%20be%20a%20way%20to%20earn%20well%20for%20my%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20390px)%2085vw%2C%20390px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11115324%2FSarfaraz1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22390%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11115324%2FSarfaraz1.jpg%20816w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11115324%2FSarfaraz1-204x300.jpg%20204w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11115324%2FSarfaraz1-696x1024.jpg%20696w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701054%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22574%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Baba%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20he%20is%20famously%20known%20on%20Youtube%2C%20has%20over%20three%20lakh%20subscribers%20and%20boasts%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98network%E2%80%99%20in%20many%20countries.%20Through%20his%20Youtube%20videos%2C%20he%20entices%20people%20into%20jobs%20abroad.%20He%20says%20he%20has%20%E2%80%98setting%E2%80%99%20with%20officials%20at%20airports%20and%20employment%20offices%20abroad.%20He%20sends%20people%20to%20other%20countries%20on%20tourist%20visas%2C%20on%20the%20promise%20that%20he%20will%20get%20it%20converted%20into%20a%20work%20visa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20called%20him%2C%20he%20explained%20that%20the%20Russian%20Army%20needs%20security%20helpers%20and%20supporting%20staff%20for%20back-end%20jobs%20to%20handle%20the%20security%20of%20army%20goods.%20He%20told%20me%20that%20the%20joinees%20will%20be%20provided%20training%20for%20three%20months.%20I%20asked%20him%20if%20it%E2%80%99s%20safe%20to%20join%20the%20Russian%20army%20as%20the%20country%20had%20been%20at%20war%20with%20Ukraine%20for%20about%20two%20years.%20He%20said%20with%20great%20confidence%20that%20the%20war%20is%20over%20as%20%E2%80%98Russia%20has%20won%20and%20taken%2040%25%20of%20Ukrainian%20territory%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20managed%20to%20gain%20my%20trust%20and%20rushed%20me%20into%20the%20decision%20by%20saying%20that%20only%20ten%20vacancies%20are%20available%20for%20this%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20team%20asked%20me%20to%20deposit%20Rs%203%20lakh%20as%20%E2%80%98service%20charge%E2%80%99%20for%20assisting%20me%20with%20a%20visa%2C%20flights%20and%20getting%20me%20to%20the%20Russian%20Army%20facility%20in%20Moscow.%20I%20somehow%20arranged%20the%20money%20with%20my%20mother%E2%80%99s%20savings%20and%20borrowed%20some%20money%20from%20my%20brother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELittle%20did%20I%20know%20that%20I%20was%20walking%20into%20a%20death%20trap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C