%20question%20of%20selling%20anything%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Neeraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Crew-and-Family-1709904528.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Zero%20electricity%20bills%20are%20possible%20with%20solar%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Crew-and-Family-1709904528.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Crew-and-Family-1709904528-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Crew-and-Family-1709904528-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Crew-and-Family-1709904528-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Crew-and-Family-1709904528-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344450%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFamilies%20are%20first%20explained%20the%20process%2C%20cost%20and%20benefits%20of%20going%20solar.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20many%20consumers%20understand%20the%20benefits%20of%20going%20solar.%20Whatever%20money%20they%20put%20into%20installing%20solar%2C%20they%E2%80%99ll%20recover%20their%20investment%20in%20three%20to%20five%20years%20depending%20on%20the%20electricity%20tariff%20and%20then%20enjoy%2020%20to%2022%20years%20of%20free%20electricity.%20However%2C%20the%20initial%20investment%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%20to%20Rs%203%20lakh%20to%20install%20a%20rooftop%20solar%20system%20is%20often%20difficult%20for%20most%20middle-class%20families%20in%20Indian%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20this