0%9CThe%20major%20issue%20that%20I%20could%20see%20was%20that%20since%20I%20was%20the%20first%20one%20to%20start%20something%20like%20this%20on%20the%20island%2C%20there%20was%20very%20little%20connectivity.%20There%20were%20no%20regular%20ferries%2C%20and%20the%20available%20ones%20were%20painfully%20slow%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20infrastructure%20of%20the%20place%20was%20very%20poor%2C%20and%20before%20Samit%20could%20begin%20work%20on%20his%20resort%2C%20he%20had%20to%20address%20the%20challenge%20of%20making%20it%20accessible%20to%20the%20world.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20there%20was%20an%20important%20lesson%20learned%20from%20this%20experience.%20Havelock%20was%20Havelock%20for%20this%20reason%20%E2%80%94%20fewer%20crowds%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335433%2Fnorthstar-school-rajkot-sustainable-design-santiniketan-open-learning-ib-school%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20nature.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20place%20is%20not%20like%20the%20Maldives%20or%20any%20other%20tourist%20destination.%20People%20come%20here%20for%20a%20truly%20natural%20experience%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20emphasises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamit%20concluded%20that%20opening%20a%20resort%20even%20deeper%20into%20the%20island%20would%20not%20be%20wise%20due%20to%20the%20connectivity%20issue.%20Therefore%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20build%20the%20property%20alongside%20the%20beach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20come%20to%20the%20island%2C%20what%20you%E2%80%99ll%20notice%20is%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20combination%20of%20thick%20woods%20and%20beaches.%20So%20I%20decided%20to%20create%20a%20resort%20that%20blends%20into%20the%20natural%20surroundings%20and%20does%20not%20disturb%20the%20wildlife%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%