the%20week%2C%20months%20of%20the%20year%2C%20and%20multiplication%20tables%20on%20the%20tips%20of%20their%20fingers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20parents%20got%20to%20see%20how%20much%20value%20we%20are%20adding%20to%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20lives.%20They%20realised%20that%20their%20children%20actually%20study%20at%20Nayi%20Disha%20and%20that%20there%20are%20people%20who%20are%20spending%20dedicated%20time%20with%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20change%20in%20mindset%20is%20refreshing.%20The%20parents%E2%80%99%20new%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334155%2Fbengaluru-ngo-dream-a-dream-educates-underprivileged-children-life-skills-happiness-curriculum-delhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eview%20of%20the%20NGO%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20space%20of%20learning%2C%20in%20contrast%20to%20seeing%20it%20as%20a%20creche%2C%20is%20a%20win%20according%20to%20Seema.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESchool%20is%20freedom%20for%20these%20children.%20Right%20from%20the%209%20am%20assembly%20and%20the%20circle%20time%20%E2%80%94%20where%20they%20share%20their%20observations%20about%20the%20weather%2C%20talk%20about%20their%20day%20and%20express%20themselves%20%E2%80%94%20to%20the%20chatter%20at%20the%20mid-day%20meal%20distribution%20and%20English%20classes%20that%20are%20conducted%20by%20volunteer%20students%20from%20colleges%20across%20Gurugram%2C%20each%20moment%20is%20a%20celebration%20of%20learning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20the%20kids%20love%20theatre%20sessions%20the%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20makes%20them%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333542%2Fupsc-cse-interview-round-tips-by-ias-officers-personality-test-toppers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econfident%20and%20outgoing%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20encourages%20them%20to%20speak%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20