20She%20took%20the%20decision%20to%20quit%20her%20job%20and%20focus%20on%20him.%20While%20she%20missed%20her%20job%2C%20she%20found%20that%20her%20son%20needed%20her%20the%20most%20at%20that%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20toyed%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342261%2Fwoman-entrepreneur-saroj-prajapati-founder-moms-magic-pickle-mango-madhya-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejoining%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20again%20at%20some%20time%2C%20but%20life%20had%20other%20plans.%20The%20results%20of%20the%20hair%20oil%20in%202020%20pleasantly%20surprised%20her.%20It%20took%20her%20back%20to%20her%20conversations%20with%20her%20grandmother%2C%20when%20she%20would%20ask%20her%20why%20she%20spent%20so%20much%20time%20making%20this%20oil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20%3Cem%3Edaadi%3C%2Fem%3E%20would%20sit%20with%20this%20iron%20%3Cem%3Ekadhai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(large%20vessel)%20every%20week%2C%20and%20spend%20hours%20stirring%20the%20oil%2C%20adding%2013%20ingredients%20one%20by%20one.%20She%20used%20to%20tell%20me%20that%20I%20would%20realise%20its%20worth%20after%20growing%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nidhi%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESure%20enough%2C%20just%20as%20the%20wise%20woman%20had%20predicted%2C%20Nidhi%20turned%20to%20her%20daadi%E2%80%99s%20recipe%20when%20she%20faced%20the%20massive%20challenge%20of%20hairfall.%20The%20duo%20made%20the%20oil%20together%2C%20which%20took%20an%20entire%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20faced%20tremendous%20hair%20fall.%20After%20using%20it%20for%20about%20two-three%20months%2C%20we%20found%20that%20our%20hairfall%20had%20greatly%20reduced%20and%20our%20hair%20was%20growing.%20I%20started%20making%20it%20for%20my%20daughter%20and%20our%20domestic%20help%2C%20who%20also%20found%20it%20greatly%20effective%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Rajni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20Tuteja-Dua%20family%20shifted%20from%20Delhi%20to%20Gurugram%2C%20into%20an%20apartment%20complex.%20It%20was%20here%20that%20Nidhi%20would%20find%20an%20opportunity%20to%20give%20shape%20to%20her%20desires.%20She%20found%20women%20here%20who%20were%20running%20small%20businesses%20from%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20mothers%2C%20Nidhi%2C%20too%2C%20had%20a%20burning%20desire%20to%20have%20a%20flourishing%20career.%20When%20she%20heard%20about%20these%20women%2C%20she%20found%20her%20window.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20always%20thought%20that%20I%20would%20join%20the%20office%20again.%20I%20missed%20my%20financial%20freedom%20and%20kept%20thinking%20of%20what%20I%20could%20do%20to%20reclaim%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nidhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajni%2C%20who%20had%20spent%20her%20life%20taking%20care%20of%20her%20children%2C%20followed%20by%20her%20grandchildren%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20harbour%20such%20aspirations%2C%20she%20shares.%20But%20when%20Nidhi%20asked%20for%20her%20help%2C%20the%20indulgent%20mother-in-law%2C%20went%20all%20in%20to%20support%20her%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20first%20started%20distributing%20the%20oil%20to%20women%20in%20our%20society.%20To%20our%20surprise%2C%20they%20kept%20coming%20back%20for%20more.%20In%20fact%2C%20our%20doorbell%20used%20to%20keep%20ringing%2C%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20Nidhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20beginning%2C%20they%20would%20pack%20the%20oil%20in%20normal%20bottles%20with%20a%20sticker.%20The%20first%20batch%20of%20one%20litre%20was%20made%20on%20a%20small%20kadhai%20and%20sold%2010%20bottles.%20As%20soon%20as%20Nidhi%20posted%20on%20a%20Whatsapp%20group%2C%20they%20were%20sold%20out%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20hours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20925px)%20100vw%2C%20925px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhii-1709647491.